sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant V as vLLM
    participant G as GPU Memory

    Note over C,G: First Request (Cache Miss)
    C->>V: Request with System Prompt (500 tokens) + Query (50 tokens)
    V->>G: Process 550 tokens
    G->>G: Cache System Prompt (500 tokens)
    V->>C: Response (Cost: 550 tokens)

    %% Blank line before second note
    Note over C,G: Subsequent Requests (Cache Hit)
    C->>V: Same System Prompt + New Query (50 tokens)
    V->>G: Retrieve cached 500 tokens
    V->>G: Process only 50 new tokens
    V->>C: Response (Cost: 50 tokens - 90% savings!)

